external_knowledge:
- 'Live stocks' refers to stocks that are currently active (is_active = 1);
- 'Items on the 'Another Watchlist'' refers to entries counted from the watchlists named 'Another Watchlist';
- 'Active researchers' refers to users with the role 'researcher' who are currently active (is_active = 1).

- "beacon lights" metaphorically refers to stocks that attract significant attention; 
- "drawing the most curious eyes" indicates the stocks with the highest access counts;
- "over the past week" corresponds to the last seven days.

